ZH: 我们需要在晚上六点前到场。
EN: We need to arrive at the venue by 6pm.

ZH: 希望你能够准时到场。
EN: I hope you can arrive on time.

ZH: 请务必在会议开始前到场。
EN: Please make sure to arrive before the meeting starts.

ZH: 你们都必须按时到场。
EN: You all must arrive on time.

ZH: 演出开始前请大家到场。
EN: Please arrive before the show starts.

ZH: 如果你不到场，就会错过很多重要信息。
EN: If you don't show up, you will miss out on a lot of important information.

ZH: 他总是迟到，希望他能够这次准时到场。
EN: He is always late, I hope he can arrive on time this time.

ZH: 请不要迟到，务必准时到场。
EN: Please do not be late, make sure to arrive on time.

ZH: 如果你不能及时到场，请提前通知我们。
EN: If you cannot arrive on time, please notify us in advance.

ZH: 如果你不能来，请至少提前一个小时告知，以便我们能做出调整。
EN: If you cannot make it, please notify us at least one hour in advance so we can make arrangements.

ZH: 请在演出开始前十分钟到场。
EN: Please arrive 10 minutes before the show starts.

ZH: 已经有许多人到场了。
EN: Many people have already arrived at the scene.

ZH: 很抱歉，出席人数少于预期，希望更多人能到场。
EN: We are sorry that the attendance is lower than expected, we hope more people can show up.

ZH: 我们需要更多的志愿者到场帮助。
EN: We need more volunteers to show up and help.

ZH: 我们正在等待所有参与者到场后开始。
EN: We are waiting for all the participants to arrive before we start.

ZH: 非常感谢您的到场和支持。
EN: Thank you very much for your presence and support.

ZH: 演讲将延迟十分钟，希望大家能耐心等待到场。
EN: The speech will be delayed by 10 minutes, we hope everyone can patiently wait until arrival.

ZH: 大家都已经到场了，可以开始了。
EN: Everyone has arrived, we can start now.

ZH: 如果有人迟到，请通知我一声。
EN: If someone is late, please let me know.

ZH: 为了节目顺利进行，请大家按时到场。
EN: In order for the program to proceed smoothly, please arrive on time.
